{"info": {"author": "l2m2", "author_email": "l2m2lq@gmail.com", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "description": "# cpcc-tool\nSome method for Software copyright application in China, including the generation of source code Word documents, source code statistics, etc.\n\n```\npip install cpcctool\n```\n\n**Example: Generate documentation for the first and last 40 pages of source code**\n\n```python\n  import uuid\n  import os\n  from cpcctool import gen_code_docx, docx_first_40_pages, docx_last_40_pages\n  src_dirs = [\n    r\"F:\\workspace\\xxx\\code1\\\",\n    r\"F:\\workspace\\xxx\\code2\\\"\n  ]\n  dst_file = str(uuid.uuid4()) + \".docx\"\n  gen_code_docx(src_dirs, dst_file)\n  dst_file = os.path.abspath(dst_file)\n  docx_first_n_pages(dst_file, r\"xxxSystem XXX V2.0.0 Source Code first 40 pages.docx\", 40)\n  docx_last_n_pages(dst_file, r\"xxxSystem XXX V2.0.0 Source Code last 40 pages.docx\", 40)\n```\n\n**Example: Statistics source code total lines**\n\n```python\nfrom cpcctool import count_code_lines\nsrc_dirs = [\n    r\"F:\\workspace\\xxx\\code1\\\",\n    r\"F:\\workspace\\xxx\\code2\\\"\n]\ncloc_exe = r\"F:\\workspace\\l2m2\\cpcc-tool\\cloc-1.84.exe\"\ncount = count_code_lines(cloc_exe, src_dirs)\nprint(count)\n```\n\n## Publish to PyPI\n\n```\npip install --user --upgrade setuptools wheel twine\npython setup.py sdist bdist_wheel\npython -m twine upload dist/*\n```\n\n## Reference\n\n- [CLOC](https://github.com/AlDanial/cloc)\n- [python-docx](https://python-docx.readthedocs.io/en/latest/)\n- [How do I delete a range (pages) in a document using VBA.](https://social.msdn.microsoft.com/Forums/office/en-US/b5b34fd3-e36b-432c-94d2-9c687e273440/how-do-i-delete-a-range-pages-in-a-document-using-vba?forum=worddev)\n\n", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/l2m2/cpcc-tool", "keywords": "", "license": "", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "cpcctool", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/cpcctool/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/cpcctool/", "project_urls": {"Homepage": "https://github.com/l2m2/cpcc-tool"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/cpcctool/0.0.3/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": ">=3.6", "summary": "CPCC Tool.", "version": "0.0.3", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <h1>cpcc-tool</h1>\n<p>Some method for Software copyright application in China, including the generation of source code Word documents, source code statistics, etc.</p>\n<pre><code>pip install cpcctool\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Example: Generate documentation for the first and last 40 pages of source code</strong></p>\n<pre>  <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"nn\">uuid</span>\n  <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"nn\">os</span>\n  <span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">cpcctool</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">gen_code_docx</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">docx_first_40_pages</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">docx_last_40_pages</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">src_dirs</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"p\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"sa\">r</span><span class=\"s2\">\"F:\\workspace\\xxx\\code1</span><span class=\"se\">\\\"</span><span class=\"s2\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"sa\">r</span><span class=\"s2\">\"F:\\workspace\\xxx\\code2</span><span class=\"se\">\\\"</span>\n  <span class=\"p\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">dst_file</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">str</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">uuid</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">uuid4</span><span class=\"p\">())</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"s2\">\".docx\"</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">gen_code_docx</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">src_dirs</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">dst_file</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">dst_file</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">os</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">path</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">abspath</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">dst_file</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">docx_first_n_pages</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">dst_file</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"sa\">r</span><span class=\"s2\">\"xxxSystem XXX V2.0.0 Source Code first 40 pages.docx\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">40</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">docx_last_n_pages</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">dst_file</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"sa\">r</span><span class=\"s2\">\"xxxSystem XXX V2.0.0 Source Code last 40 pages.docx\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"mi\">40</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<p><strong>Example: Statistics source code total lines</strong></p>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">cpcctool</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">count_code_lines</span>\n<span class=\"n\">src_dirs</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"p\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"sa\">r</span><span class=\"s2\">\"F:\\workspace\\xxx\\code1</span><span class=\"se\">\\\"</span><span class=\"s2\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"sa\">r</span><span class=\"s2\">\"F:\\workspace\\xxx\\code2</span><span class=\"se\">\\\"</span>\n<span class=\"p\">]</span>\n<span class=\"n\">cloc_exe</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"sa\">r</span><span class=\"s2\">\"F:\\workspace\\l2m2\\cpcc-tool\\cloc-1.84.exe\"</span>\n<span class=\"n\">count</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">count_code_lines</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">cloc_exe</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">src_dirs</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">count</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<h2>Publish to PyPI</h2>\n<pre><code>pip install --user --upgrade setuptools wheel twine\npython setup.py sdist bdist_wheel\npython -m twine upload dist/*\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Reference</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/AlDanial/cloc\" rel=\"nofollow\">CLOC</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://python-docx.readthedocs.io/en/latest/\" rel=\"nofollow\">python-docx</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://social.msdn.microsoft.com/Forums/office/en-US/b5b34fd3-e36b-432c-94d2-9c687e273440/how-do-i-delete-a-range-pages-in-a-document-using-vba?forum=worddev\" rel=\"nofollow\">How do I delete a range (pages) in a document using VBA.</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 7102913, "releases": {"0.0.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "9ab08e266334b23dc4f1a5ede3f4fb94", "sha256": "adf611db63f4dd59db7f9ff6d6859f20108745db3aa27f0422b165388b3eaad8"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "cpcctool-0.0.1-py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "9ab08e266334b23dc4f1a5ede3f4fb94", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "py3", "requires_python": ">=3.6", "size": 5855, "upload_time": "2019-12-25T06:29:25", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2019-12-25T06:29:25.490377Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/d3/bd/f8cf48e1e52760b2762d4348e7b379a1a178ff9ff9b2a0303bb2fa15067f/cpcctool-0.0.1-py3-none-any.whl", "yanked": false}, {"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "4c41b4d490168d3952903408635dfdd4", "sha256": "9bff9f6b50c889d715b4b9122a0a94e4395f6959c5b0cb6db29218a1e47c5a31"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "cpcctool-0.0.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "4c41b4d490168d3952903408635dfdd4", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": ">=3.6", "size": 3689,